# IMPORTANT: When making a PR you must follow the rules in CONTRIBUTING.md

## PR requirements (CI-enforced)

- Every PR must add a new task file: `docs/tasks/YYYY-MM-DD-short-description.md`
- Every PR must update: `CHANGELOG.md`

Example task file: `docs/tasks/2025-12-29-add-cursorrules-and-pr-template.md`

